{
  "stem": "21004.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have to pass by-- a little further down, I have to pass by a bridge in the road.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's no way for me to pass the bridge because it was a lake going.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have to go through that bridge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And through that bridge, they have lights on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, before that bridge, I saw where they were making from flour a mill, where they were making flour.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went on to that place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were bags from flour there, laying bags from flour.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took the bag from flour for me one, and for him one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two and two bags.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I made his face with flour, and I made my-- my face with flour because we were-- our clothes was the clothes from the hard labor camp with stripes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So make him all the clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Dirty up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And put the bags.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just to get out through that bridge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And later, we walked only at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only at night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this helped us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For some people were go and walking, they didn't recognize-- people going from the mill from work, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So later on, walking for two days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Walking only at night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then the third day, when I was walking through the village, it was 12:00 midnight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was never walked before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And 12:00-- we didn't realize three guys, three Ukrainian guys, jumped on us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- and I was talking to him only Ukrainian, not Jewish at all, or Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they jumped on us and they grabbed us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "How-- somehow they recognized us or they recognized maybe the clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they grabbed us on the [GERMAN], to come on way to the commandos.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "To the German commandos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Taking us.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, here, listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
